To do so, we have selected relevant atom-atom interactions based on elemental parameters to generate molecule-level descriptors that closely describe their impact on target properties. We use in this study 8 descriptors in total. Four descriptors (number of atoms, cell volume, molecular mass and formation heat) are picked up from the C2DB database. Four additional descriptors were created according the following procedure. One descriptor (electronegativity) was calculated by using empirical equation26. For instance, the electronegativity of a molecular formula AaBb\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
